#heading(outlined: false, bookmarked: true)[Abstract]
The abstract should be a concise summary of the thesis in English. It should include the
problem statement, the objectives, the methodology, and the key results and conclusions.
The abstract should be no longer than one page and should be written in a way that is
accessible to a broad audience.
